<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Reward2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Reward,</orth> vb. to recompense, to requite; in a good a well as a bad sense: <cit><quote>r. not hospitality with such black payment,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 575" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 575</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>which heaven and fortune still --s with plagues,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. IV, 3, 31</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>they are but lightly --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.157" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 157</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ing my dependents,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 3.134.157" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 134</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.153" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 153</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.153" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 153</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.3.7" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.236" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 236</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.123" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 123</bibl> (Ff <emph>repays</emph>). <bibl n="shak. h8 3.1.133" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 1, 133</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.9.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 9, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.2.131" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.82" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.130" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 130</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.6.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 6, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.317" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 317</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.7.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 7, 14</bibl>.
